column2: SELECT b.*, a.ra as sdss_ra, a.dec as sdss_dec, a.z as sdss_z, a.snMedian_r as sdss_sn_r, a.plate as sdss_plate, a.mjd as sdss_mjd, a.fiberID as sdss_fiberID into mydb.galpair_A1#_sdss_dr1# from mydb.galpair_A1#_sdss as b CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (ra, dec, #) as c join DR1#.specObjAll as a on a.bestObjID = c.ObjID
